These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, zombie, superhero, satire
1. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
2. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
6. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person watching zombie movies##7
8. the chinese and the person watching satire movies have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person watching fantasy movies have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | superhero   | satire     | zombie | fantasy  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, snowmobile, car
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling and the person driving the motorbike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
8. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | car     | snowmobile    | trike | motorbike    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, milk
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, poker, scrabble
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
2. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8
8. the person drinking cola and the person playing snooker have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola    | fanta   | coffee    | milk  |
| Food       | snooker | scrabble | mah-jongg | poker |

