.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, cola, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking lemonade and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | lemonade | cola | almond-milk  | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

