.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, hip-hop
City: venice, london, new-york, paris
1. the fan country is not the person traveling to new-york##6
2. the person traveling to venice and the fan blues have different parity positions##9
3. the person traveling to london and the fan classical have different parity positions##9
4. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
6. the fan classical is not the person traveling to london##6
7. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan classical##5
8. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the fan blues##1
9. the person traveling to paris is not the fan hip-hop##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | blues | country | hip-hop  | classical |
| Pet           | london   | venice     | new-york | paris      |

