5. the person watching superhero movies and the writer have different parity positions##9
6. the lawyer is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
7. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
8. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the doctor##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation | scientific | superhero |
| Nationality   | doctor        | lawyer    | writer   | journalist |

