2. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
3. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person playing canasta##7
4. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person eating mango##7
5. the person playing chess is not the person eating tomato##6
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
