3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who growszinnia have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person who growsiris is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
