.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, basketball, cycling-polo, cycling
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, magic-tricks, reading
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
 7. the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling-polo##8
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | basketball    | cycling-polo        | cycling   | skiing      |
| Hobby      | reading | magic-tricks | fishing | board-games |

 